{
  "stem": "5275.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And even though I didn't understand a word of what he said-- it was in German-- I was very impressed and I understood what was going on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As we were leaving the theatre, we were approached by two Germans, and I don't know how they figured out that we were non-German.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But again, they took us to the side, and I had to show my penis, and my mother had to give them a golden bracelet.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they let us go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] [SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, we were released there, and OK, so I went to-- I went back to Kielce to the factory, and my mother stayed in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, this was the time, I think, that my mother should have left Krakow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had an opportunity to cross the border and go into Russia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was given that opportunity, and she refused because she didn't want to abandon me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was a big mistake.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Again, my mother found some Polish baron-- or not a baron, no, it's like a-- not quite a prince, but a count, a count, Polish count.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And amazingly enough, the Germans didn't confiscated his belongings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he-- so she realized that I was undernourished and she somehow got permission from them to go visit them for one week.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they fed me and they fed me-- for one week, meals five times a day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you know, I was hungry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then I realized what was the matter-- because when I was in Kielce, I was eating this huge pot of soup in the-- at noontime, and a huge one in the evening.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my stomach was full.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When I ate, instead eggs and cheeses and meats, there was nothing fooling my stomach, and I felt hungry.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
